Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.25,0:01:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里得到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是障眼法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再吃同样的招式了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光弹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是诱饵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一波接一波
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 贤者之石的力量真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也用过 所以非常清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此才不理解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不把那个力量用在取回自己的身体上？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若有石头的话 从我们手中逃走非常简单
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全逃脱后 再用石头恢复你们原来的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你们的旅程不就能结束了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 无法拯救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了达成长年的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了得到什么就必须舍弃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只有两个选择？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恢复原来的身体和
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:03:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:04:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能选择其中之一太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么没有既能恢复原来的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又能拯救大家的选项呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等价交换的法则是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为不被原则束缚追求可能性这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在人类进步中也是必须的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能够实现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就会作为新的道理被世间认同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 另一个可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不仅无法恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也无法拯救大家的选项也准备一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 皮肤下面能行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死也…真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超麻烦 要拿出真本事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姆斯壮少将
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丢下武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个大个子是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…打中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是什么速度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怠惰 斯洛乌斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直就很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的看到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能隐约看到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个重量居然有这样的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是犯规
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我是速度最快的人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚力士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为太快了连自己也无法控制吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于…打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强烈的意志相互碰撞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能演奏出这么美妙的音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯·艾尔利克还在附近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能就这样死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是障眼法 真没情调
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.09,0:07:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过 根据味道就能知道你的所在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始才是人类顽强的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.47,0:08:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使有贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为仅凭一个人就能战胜我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石头到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个土尘的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了调查风向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的嗅觉无法察觉到的下风处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做什么小动作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从背后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么重的伤怎么还能动？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马可医生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是冰淇淋的卡车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 别看漏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术真是便利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要改变车子的外观是小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东西南北
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令部所有的门都被封锁了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 要强行突破吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:09:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 在外面暴乱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:10:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就交给布里克斯的那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走秘密通道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里开始分头行动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们陪着夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向预定场所前进
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉厚救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（好痛…好痛）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是脚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄准它们的脚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚力士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 只是脱臼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是骨折而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点杀掉…去睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利使他犹豫了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这家伙怎么可能考虑这些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你说的 人类很顽强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你们无法胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我们的父亲大人在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,况且
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前 你们必须对付现在这个局面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤基？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.11,0:13:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你居然会来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能只让你们显酷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也让我摆摆酷 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤基大人让最强的人造人吃了一招
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他吃了一招
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这车子是哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是金普利坐的车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让司机先休息一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 马可医生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上嘴巴 全速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不打算和那个怪物正面战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去中央都市市内
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在被它追上之前和爱德他们会合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:14:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒那个父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有勇气不逃跑的人类 真是非常好骗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这西服的颜色变得很好看了 金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百兽之王可不是浪得虚名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵从弱肉强食的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻轻松松就把你的喉管给咬断了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然人类是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可有可无的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你常说 想看看世界会选择哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.81,0:16:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 却要死在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉是耻辱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会在我的体内继续活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底…发生什么事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚力士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正它会自己冲过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要等着它过来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 能站起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面好像对我下了枪杀命令呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可让人很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姆斯壮家要由我来继承
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得先办完手续才能死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多余的担心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房子会自动转让给马斯坦古
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种约定居然没和家人商量就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起你这种没用的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是那家伙要比你强上一丁点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是对待救命恩人的态度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌袭吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是马斯坦古队？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中枪也不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里克斯兵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把我的精兵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那种苍白的家伙相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕和这个是同类
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:19:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是向你们发令的家伙在操纵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有听说过这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你们知不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方似乎是无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我们姐弟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能对抗那些怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说 打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枪杀我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后成为怪物的饵食吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:20:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说 协助我们杀死怪物？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你自己的脑子好好想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.80,0:20:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙是注入了贤者之石的人偶兵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那么容易死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧看吧 因为你总是逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又让我吸收了一些 变得更强了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.74,0:20:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:21:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人偶大军来了是比较麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你一个人的话可以轻松逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这人偶被注入了贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.41,0:21:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然长生不老的秘密在贤者之石上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了拯救部族
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.93,0:21:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要获得长生不老之术
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.09,0:21:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（好痛 好痛）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还会出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,针要用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的唾液也快干了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.82,0:21:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.08,0:22:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.54,0:22:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你在的地方总是很吵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我帮你收拾一下比较好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.81,0:22:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.18,0:24:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,当人抵达真实之时
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.38,0:24:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就会暴露赤裸的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.74,0:24:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,无法阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.85,0:24:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,也无选择的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.47,0:24:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.22,0:24:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.81,0:24:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第53话 复仇的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.52,0:24:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把所有的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.26,0:24:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部烧尽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.84,0:00:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:07.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}终于找到了  全新的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:11.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}日月却来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:16.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}我前往的地方  不是“未来”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:20.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}仅仅不停地追赶着“过去”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:26.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}不停地鸣响着 那过去的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:31.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}仿佛无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:36.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}差不多了吧  那厌倦搜索的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:41.56,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}丢掉心里的纠结
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:46.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  总有会停的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:52.03,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这么漫长  却如此冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:57.32,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  为什么会选择我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:01:02.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}笼罩着我  真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:06.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  已经忘了停
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:12.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天依然持续下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:17.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}在默默撑开的雨伞下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:28.90,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}接近那温暖的怀抱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】

Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.21,0:22:41.75,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur2}从那天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:46.01,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}就决定不再哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:51.56,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur2}即使承担再多的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.56,0:22:56.69,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}仍有无法原谅的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.14,0:23:00.11,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经无法回到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.11,0:23:02.61,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那平凡的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:07.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还没有做成任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:12.95,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的记忆之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.95,0:23:18.83,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}又有一块  消逝而去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:21.84,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回望今日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.84,0:23:24.59,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想变得更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.59,0:23:29.72,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}期望这个声音总有一天可以传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:32.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:34.81,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在风停止的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:39.52,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}仰望天空追寻着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.27,0:23:46.86,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}在黎明前散发的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:52.41,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}将会变成彩虹
